  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK868">
<l>kuṇaṉilaṉāyk kuṟṟam palavāyiṉ māṟṟārk </l>
<l>kiṉaṉilaṉā mēmāp puṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He will become friendless who is without (any good) qualities. and whose faults are many (such a character) is a help to (his) foes.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
